t: Praise*pn the Lord!*s Praise*ln God in His sanctuary; Praise*ln Him in His mighty expanse.
Praise*ln Him for His mighty deeds; Praise*ln Him according to His excellent greatness.
Praise*ln Him with trumpet sound; Praise*ln Him with harp and lyre.
Praise*ln Him with timbrel and dancing; Praise*ln Him with stringed instruments and pipe.
Praise*ln Him with loud cymbals; Praise*ln Him with resounding cymbals.
Let*ln everything that has breath praise the Lord.*s Praise*ln the Lord!*s
